room_title: Escape room "Loose Sleuth" by PuzzleWorks in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_address: 550 Vandalia St. Suite 311 Saint Paul, MN 55114
room_description: While investigating a recent string of crimes, our top detective has gone missing and his office has been ransacked. The cops are on their way, and you have access to the crime scene for one hour. Can you make sense of the clues and find out what happened to him before the police arrive?
